- add [j] to "minuteness"

At this point I should probably mention that Lovecraft isn't for the QS novice unless an Orthodox version is handy; [s@bt@rin] seemed like "sub tureen" (unexpected, but I've been thrown bigger curve balls before) until I flipped over to the Orthodox version and read "subterrene".
